oject emphasizing the importance of stem ms taitz was a board member of girls who code for  years and is now as a board member of fred wilson’s the new york city foundation for computer science contact colle capital copyright all rights reserved   colle capital  developed by ataki solutions contact us please use the form below to send your messageinquirysuggestion thanks send start typing and press enter to search adam sagerdavid soloff hope s taitz joins diamond resorts board of directors hotel news bitac® events casino resorts aug   more info sold out for suppliers purchasing  design west oct   more info  supplier spots left owners event dec   more info  supplier spots left building your hospitality business   are you a member log in  or  sign up membership   member log inenews samplesign up  free features   home pagearticle librarymember pollsevent calendarmember feedbackcontact us the radio show this week in hospitality follow us on twitter hotelinteractiv   send a summary and link to this article to email  required  improper email your name  required your email  required  improper email bot test  required to pass the bot test please type the white text that you see in the gray box this helps us prevent spammers from abusing the system  to confirm please type the white text that you see in the gray box printable version hope s taitz joins diamond resorts board of directors monday august   bookmark this we are on twitter hotelinteractiv diamond resorts international the board of directors of diamond resorts international inc announced the appointment of hope s taitz as an independent director effective today ms taitzs appointment expands the board to nine directors ms taitz will be a member of the compensation committee “hope brings a wealth of knowledge and experience to our board her background will be of great value to both our shareholders and our people” said david f palmer president and ceo of diamond resorts international inc hope s taitz is currently the 